this concoction

25:01.132 --> 25:02.534
will slow down the infected.

25:04.936 --> 25:06.338
- Tastes like chicken soup.

25:06.404 --> 25:08.440
- That's because
it is chicken soup.

25:08.506 --> 25:13.445
- ♪

25:15.247 --> 25:16.748
- Um, I don't
know if this is--

25:16.815 --> 25:18.316
- Duck and load people.

25:22.053 --> 25:23.688
Look sharp.
They can be anywhere.

25:29.227 --> 25:30.729
- Luna! Three o'clock!

25:30.795 --> 25:32.330
- [groans]

25:32.397 --> 25:33.431
- [yells]

25:35.267 --> 25:37.502
- LINCOLN:
Lisa! Six o'clock.

25:37.569 --> 25:38.703
- [yells]

25:40.605 --> 25:42.073
- [car crashing]

25:44.276 --> 25:45.377
- Leni! Nine o'clock.

25:45.443 --> 25:47.145
- Lincoln, make up your mind.

25:47.212 --> 25:48.647
What time is it?

25:48.713 --> 25:50.415
- No! Behind you!

25:50.482 --> 25:51.816
- Ah!

25:51.883 --> 25:53.151
Want a tissue?

25:54.185 --> 25:56.221
- Lincoln, where is your heart?

25:56.288 --> 25:57.822
- Where is your brain?

25:57.889 --> 25:59.658
We're trying to stay alive here.

25:59.724 --> 26:01.059
- Dudes, help!

26:01.126 --> 26:02.394
- [groaning]

26:02.460 --> 26:06.698
- Ah!

26:07.966 --> 26:09.968
- [groaning]

26:10.035 --> 26:11.703
- Evacuate!

26:11.770 --> 26:15.573
- [groaning]

26:17.208 --> 26:19.811
Think, Loud! You've seen
a million zombie movies.

26:19.878 --> 26:23.248
Wait! I've got it.
Urgh...aargh.

26:23.315 --> 26:25.317
- Whoa.
Lincoln's one of them now.

26:25.383 --> 26:26.651
- In that case...
- [gun cocking]

26:26.718 --> 26:29.087
- Hold your fire.
I'm just trying to blend in.

26:29.154 --> 26:31.056
Come on.
It's your ticket to freedom.

26:31.122 --> 26:36.127
- [groaning]

26:39.464 --> 26:41.766
- Aww.
They sound so sick.

26:41.833 --> 26:43.535
Do you guys need a cough drop?

26:43.601 --> 26:44.636
- [groaning]

26:46.071 --> 26:49.641
- Leni, you're putting the squad
in jeopardy and I won't have it.

26:49.708 --> 26:51.109
Wait. Where's Lucy?

26:54.412 --> 26:56.548
Dang it.
We lost another one.

26:56.614 --> 26:58.016
She was so young.

26:58.083 --> 26:59.351
Healthy Loud to safe haven.

26:59.417 --> 27:01.086
We're down
to three survivors.

27:01.152 --> 27:02.420
- CLYDE: Sorry to hear it,
Healthy Loud.

27:02.487 --> 27:03.888
Everything's set on this end.

27:03.955 --> 27:05.357
Quick question
for the heal meals,

27:05.423 --> 27:07.292
does everyone eat guacamole?

27:07.359 --> 27:10.261
- Affirmative.
And, hey, Safe Haven, thanks.

27:10.328 --> 27:13.498
We're tasting freedom
in three, two...

27:13.565 --> 27:14.599
- [groaning]

27:14.666 --> 27:15.767
- Aargh!

27:15.834 --> 27:17.602
The virus has jumped species.

27:17.669 --> 27:20.038
- We can still escape
through the back door!

27:20.105 --> 27:21.373
- But, Lincoln...

27:22.741 --> 27:24.876
- Once we're out the door,
keep a tight formation.

27:24.943 --> 27:26.077
- [gasping]

27:26.144 --> 27:28.346
- Reroute! Reroute!

27:28.413 --> 27:29.814
- To the parental dwelling!

27:29.881 --> 27:31.216
- [crickets chirping]

27:31.282 --> 27:33.184
- Mom and Dad's room.

27:34.586 --> 27:35.720
- Move! Move!

27:37.455 --> 27:38.990
- Dad! The house is infected.

27:39.057 --> 27:41.059
We need to get out
through your window.

27:41.126 --> 27:44.162
- [groaning]

27:44.229 --> 27:45.797
- [gasping]
- We've got a hostile.

27:45.864 --> 27:46.998
- [door opens]
- [gasping]

27:47.065 --> 27:49.234
- [groaning]

27:49.300 --> 27:51.669
- Aww.
Mom doesn't feel well.

27:51.736 --> 27:53.238
She just needs a hug.

27:53.304 --> 27:54.873
- Leni! Stand down!

27:54.939 --> 27:56.007
- [groaning]

27:56.074 --> 27:59.044
- Mom, I hate to do
this, but--

27:59.110 --> 28:00.512
Arrgh! Noodle jam!

28:00.578 --> 28:02.514
Why did you have
to use chunky style?

28:02.580 --> 28:04.949
- It's heartier.
- [groaning]

28:05.016 --> 28:07.352
- Aah! Lucy's infected!

28:07.419 --> 28:09.954
- Again,
this is just how I look,

28:10.021 --> 28:12.157
and you're welcome
for the rescue.

28:12.223 --> 28:14.526
- [groaning]

28:18.463 --> 28:19.898
- That should hold 'em.

28:19.964 --> 28:21.966
- [groaning]
- Aww. Poor guys.

28:22.033 --> 28:23.168
They need a tissue.

28:23.234 --> 28:24.402
- Good idea.

28:26.871 --> 28:28.440
- [groaning]

28:28.506 --> 28:30.575
- Lincoln, you could have
just handed it to them.

28:30.642 --> 28:32.310
- Fall out!
- But what about our--

28:33.945 --> 28:35.280
- CLYDE:
Healthy Loud! Come in.

28:35.346 --> 28:36.915
- Safe Haven,
this is Healthy Loud.

28:36.981 --> 28:40.018
We are just about out the door
and heading to your location.

28:40.085 --> 28:41.186
- That's why I'm calling.

28:41.252 --> 28:43.588
I'm afraid there's
a bit of a crisis here.

28:43.655 --> 28:45.290
- What's that, Clyde?
Go again.

28:45.356 --> 28:49.427
- I said health issues,
possible casualty unless...

28:49.494 --> 28:52.197
- Unless what?
Clyde!

28:52.263 --> 28:54.065
Dang it! The walkie's dead!

28:54.132 --> 28:57.335
We can't leave without knowing
if Safe Haven is truly safe.

28:57.402 --> 28:58.870
- I have batteries in my room.

28:58.937 --> 29:00.138
- Looks like we're going up.

29:00.205 --> 29:01.940
Loud, you take front!

29:02.006 --> 29:03.908
- We're all Loud.

29:03.975 --> 29:05.944
- Fine.
Just follow me.

29:08.012 --> 29:11.683
- Uh, let's see, graduated
cylinder, uh, test tube,

29:11.749 --> 29:13.051
enriched uranium.

29:13.118 --> 29:15.854
Here we are.
Two fresh double As.

29:15.920 --> 29:17.422
- LILY: [groaning]

29:17.489 --> 29:19.858
- Don't make any
sudden movements.

29:19.924 --> 29:21.759
- [laughs]

29:21.826 --> 29:22.827
[sneezes]

29:22.894 --> 29:24.696
- Aww. Poor baby.

29:26.231 --> 29:27.365
- [sneezes]

29:28.299 --> 29:30.568
- Incoming!
Hit the deck!

29:31.836 --> 29:33.104
Forgive me Lily!

29:33.171 --> 29:35.540
- No!
- What is wrong with you?

29:35.607 --> 29:38.510
- Our family may be turning
into gross, snotty sickies.

29:38.576 --> 29:41.079
But you are turning
into a monster.

29:41.146 --> 29:42.580
- I'm trying to save us.

29:42.647 --> 29:45.316
And I'm tired of you
acting like Mother Teresa.

29:45.383 --> 29:46.518
- Shows what you know.

29:46.584 --> 29:48.453
Our mother's name is Rita.

29:52.090 --> 29:54.359
- Soup in the hole!

29:57.595 --> 29:59.364
If you two ninnies
are done bickering,

29:59.430 --> 30:01.633
I'd like to go taste
that guacamole.

30:05.336 --> 30:06.871
- Safe Haven, we're back in.

30:06.938 --> 30:08.940
What is this crisis
you were talking about?

30:09.007 --> 30:11.109
- I made a peanut sauce
for the Santé Fe egg rolls.

30:11.176 --> 30:13.978
But, then, I realized someone
might have a food allergy.

30:14.045 --> 30:15.246
- That's the food crisis?

30:15.313 --> 30:17.215
We're fighting
for our lives, Clyde.

30:17.282 --> 30:19.117
No one has a food allergy.

30:19.184 --> 30:20.618
- That's a relief,
'cause this sauce

30:20.685 --> 30:22.153
really ties the dish together.

30:22.220 --> 30:23.688
Safe Haven out.

30:23.755 --> 30:24.756
- Roll out!

30:29.928 --> 30:32.564
- We'll be tasting
freedom in three, two--

30:32.630 --> 30:34.532
- Hey! The bubble is back.

30:37.569 --> 30:40.004
- Okay. Now I'm sick.

30:40.071 --> 30:41.940
See the difference?

30:42.006 --> 30:43.975
- No.
- No.

30:44.042 --> 30:45.410
- [sneezes]

30:45.476 --> 30:48.079
- Argh!
Now the doorknob's infected.

30:48.146 --> 30:49.681
- Uh, don't panic.

30:49.747 --> 30:51.216
I'm sure we'll find
a way out of this...

30:51.282 --> 30:52.650
- [sneezes]

30:52.717 --> 30:54.319
- Dang it.

30:54.385 --> 30:56.154
- [groaning]

30:56.221 --> 30:57.622
- Leni, help me with the table.

30:57.689 --> 31:00.358
- Are you finally gonna
be nice and make them a meal?

31:00.425 --> 31:01.659
- Not exactly.

31:05.063 --> 31:06.331
This doesn't look good, Leni.

31:06.397 --> 31:08.032
There's no way
out of this house.

31:08.099 --> 31:09.434
- Too bad we're not dogs.

31:09.500 --> 31:11.302
Then we could use
Charles's door.

31:11.369 --> 31:12.804
- That's it.
- You go.

31:12.870 --> 31:15.173
I'm gonna stay here
and take care of the sick.

31:15.240 --> 31:17.008
- Don't be a fool.
They're gone.

31:17.075 --> 31:19.277
We have to start a new
world without them.

31:19.344 --> 31:20.645
They'd want it that way.

31:20.712 --> 31:22.814
- I can't.
But don't worry about me.

31:22.880 --> 31:25.617
If I wear a mask
and I'm careful, I'll be okay.

31:25.683 --> 31:27.585
- I may not always agree
with you, Loud,

31:27.652 --> 31:30.588
but I respect you.
Good luck.

31:35.226 --> 31:36.594
- Nah, too blah.

31:36.661 --> 31:37.695
- [groaning]
- [table scraping]

31:37.762 --> 31:40.265
- Too flashy.
Ooh! Perfect!

31:40.331 --> 31:41.566
Goes with my outfit.

31:41.633 --> 31:44.702
- Urgh. Leni! Duck!

31:44.769 --> 31:45.603
- [sneezes]

31:45.670 --> 31:47.972
- A duck? Where?
Is it sick?

31:48.039 --> 31:50.141
- Noooo!

31:51.776 --> 31:54.412
- Lincoln, you saved me. Why?

31:54.479 --> 31:55.780
- 'Cause you've got
a good heart,

31:55.847 --> 31:58.283
and you deserve to survive
more than I do.

31:58.349 --> 31:59.617
- [sneezes]

31:59.684 --> 32:00.918
Dang it.

32:00.985 --> 32:03.788
- [groaning]

32:05.723 --> 32:07.792
- Well, the escape
mission was a bust.

32:07.859 --> 32:09.460
But just because the Louds
are infected

32:09.527 --> 32:10.828
doesn't mean that
they're not human.

32:10.895 --> 32:13.765
Plus, I hate to see all
this good food go to waste.

32:16.134 --> 32:17.935
Who wants Santa Fe egg rolls?

32:18.002 --> 32:19.270
- [groaning]

32:19.337 --> 32:20.471
- Don't forget the peanut sauce.

32:20.538 --> 32:22.040
It's to die for.

32:22.106 --> 32:23.074
Oops! [nervous laugh]

32:23.141 --> 32:23.975
Poor choice of words.

32:28.746 --> 32:30.281
- ♪ Cramped inside
this tiny space ♪

32:30.348 --> 32:32.817
♪ May sound bad,
but ain't the case ♪

32:32.884 --> 32:35.420
♪ In the Loud house ♪

32:35.486 --> 32:38.256
♪ Duck and dodge
and push and shove ♪

32:38.323 --> 32:40.591
♪ That's the way
we show our love ♪

32:40.658 --> 32:43.461
♪ In the Loud house ♪

32:43.528 --> 32:44.729
♪ Laundry piles
stacked up high ♪

32:44.796 --> 32:46.230
♪ Hand-me-downs
that make me cry ♪

32:46.297 --> 32:47.398
♪ Stand in line to take a pee ♪

32:47.465 --> 32:48.966
♪ Never any privacy ♪

32:49.033 --> 32:51.536
♪ Chaos with eleven kids ♪

32:51.602 --> 32:54.038
♪ That's the way it always is ♪

32:54.105 --> 32:55.740
♪ In the Loud House ♪♪

32:55.807 --> 32:57.475
- ♪
